        <h2>Welcome to Shaldon, one of Devon's most beautiful villages</h2>
        <p>Nestled on the southern bank of the River Teign estuary, Shaldon is an unspoiled coastal village of colour-washed fishermen's cottages, winding lanes and a sheltered sandy beach. It has captured the hearts of visitors for generations, yet retains a quiet, genuine character that belongs firmly to the community who live here.</p>
        <p>Whether you're planning a short break, a longer stay, or looking for local news and community resources, this guide brings together everything Shaldon has to offer in one place.</p>
