          <h3>Christmas Lights Switch-On</h3>
          <p>The village comes alive for the annual Christmas lights ceremony on The Strand. Carols, mulled wine, festive stalls and the switching on of the village tree lights.</p>
          <span class="event-tag">Festive</span>
        </div>
      </div>
