<!-- ============================================================ ACTIVITIES -->
<section class="section" id="activities">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">Explore</span>
      <h2>Things to Do in Shaldon</h2>
      <p>Whether you're after wildlife, water sports, gentle walks or simply a beach to yourself, Shaldon delivers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="activities-grid">
      <div class="activity-card">
        <div class="activity-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 12c1.5-2 3-2 4.5 0s3 2 4.5 0 3-2 4.5 0 3 2 4.5 0"/><path d="M2 17c1.5-2 3-2 4.5 0s3 2 4.5 0 3-2 4.5 0 3 2 4.5 0"/><path d="M12 2v5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Ness Beach</h3>
        <p>A sheltered shingle and sand beach at the foot of The Ness headland, reached through a tunnel cut through the red sandstone cliff.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="activity-card">
        <div class="activity-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 17l4-8 4 4 4-6 4 10"/><path d="M2 20h20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Teignmouth Ferry</h3>
        <p>Take the historic passenger ferry across the estuary to Teignmouth. Running for centuries, it's one of the oldest river crossings in England.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="activity-card">
        <div class="activity-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="8" r="5"/><path d="M11 13v8M8 18h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Shaldon Wildlife Trust</h3>
        <p>A charming small zoo overlooking the Teign estuary, home to rare and endangered animals from around the world. A wonderful family outing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="activity-card">
        <div class="activity-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 17l5-5 4 4 5-7 4 8"/><path d="M3 3v18h18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>The Ness Walks</h3>
        <p>Explore the dramatic Ness headland with its red sandstone cliffs and sweeping views across the bay towards Dartmoor and the open coast.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="activity-card">
        <div class="activity-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 16s2-2 5-2 5 2 8 2 5-2 5-2V5s-2 2-5 2-5-2-8-2-5 2-5 2v11z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Water Sports</h3>
        <p>The sheltered estuary is ideal for kayaking, paddleboarding and sailing. Equipment hire and tuition available from the beach during summer months.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="activity-card">
        <div class="activity-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Heritage Trail</h3>
        <p>Follow the self-guided heritage trail through winding lanes, past Georgian townhouses, the old quay and St Peter's Church high above the village.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="activity-card">
        <div class="activity-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Sea Fishing</h3>
        <p>The Teign estuary and open Devon coast offer excellent sea fishing. Charter boats operate seasonally for half or full-day trips from the beach.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="activity-card">
        <div class="activity-icon">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="3"/><path d="M6 9v12M18 9v12M12 3v18M9 12h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Birdwatching</h3>
        <p>The Teign Estuary is nationally important for wading birds and wildfowl. Kingfishers, egrets, herons and dunlin are regular sightings year-round.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

